%% Shooting Sub-State Machine (inside SHOOT_AT_HUB or SHOOT_AT_OUTPOST)
%% Reflects actual code in SuperStructure.updateShooterStates()
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PREPARING

    %% Readiness check runs every cycle
    PREPARING --> FIRING : Flywheel AT_SETPOINT<br>AND Hood AT_SETPOINT<br>AND drivetrain aligned
    FIRING --> PREPARING : Flywheel loses speed<br>OR hood loses position<br>OR alignment lost

    %% Exit back to SuperStructure IDLE
    PREPARING --> [*] : SuperState leaves<br>SHOOT_AT_HUB / SHOOT_AT_OUTPOST
    FIRING --> [*] : SuperState leaves<br>SHOOT_AT_HUB / SHOOT_AT_OUTPOST

    note right of PREPARING : Flywheel spins to ShotCalculator RPM<br>Hood moves to ShotCalculator angle<br>Drivetrain aligns to target<br>Kicker & Indexer OFF
    note right of FIRING : Kicker runs at 4500 RPM<br>Indexer feeds at 40% duty cycle
